
---

## 2. `cli.py`（命令行入口示例）

```python
import argparse
from my_tool.utils import greet

def main():
    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description="My Tool CLI")
    parser.add_argument("command", help="Command to run (e.g., greet)")
    parser.add_argument("name", nargs="?", help="Name for greeting")
    args = parser.parse_args()

    if args.command == "greet":
        print(greet(args.name or "User"))
    else:
        print("Unknown command")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
